The '''Arena of Doom''' was a gladiator arena owned by [[Mondo-Mod]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] it was shut down by [[Luminara Unduli/Legends|Luminara Unduli]] and [[Barriss Offee/Legends|Barriss Offee]] after a winning ten million credit bet cleared the owners accounts, resulting in the closure. It had many different contestants including giant aliens and robots. One of the warriors at the arena was the [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droid]] [[Evil Supreme]].

